node.text:
Muse @natalee.007 
We arrived in the Maldives to shoot a new episode for MAVRIN magazine. @sunsiyamvilureef hotel has lots of awesome locations. A tropical green island where villas are neatly hidden from prying eyes 😌
📸 @mavrinstudios 
for @mavrinmag 
🌴 @sunsiyamresorts
